        "Dear Manohar,",
        "My name is Vishal Bhat and I am from Jammu, India. I am writing this letter to you with reference to the advertisement about microbiology practical course seminar in your K. P. college, London. I saw this notice in the local newspaper last week. I am interested in this course work as my background is Bachelor\u2019s in microbiology and this course will help to get a job in food industry, therefore I have decided to join this course to sharp my career objective.",
